
Version: 2.6
SVN Revision: 939

Date: March 19, 2008

Details:

- support for historical team data (no more need to wipe the database after a season)
- roster deadlines
- time before automatic approval of scores is per-league configurable
- email generated in more places
- first implementation of a generic method for sending email
- streamlining of the registration process for both users and admins
- handling of servers in different time zones than the league

